<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/icon.svg" type="image/x-icon" />
    <!-- styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/theme-switch.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/room.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/modal.css">
    <!-- scripts -->
    <script src="/scripts/theme-switch.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/scripts/main.js" defer type="module"></script>
    <!-- fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>rocket.q - Perguntas e Respostas</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="room" class="content">
      <header>
        <a href="/">
          <div class="logo">
            <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="Logo da página">
            rocket<span>.</span>q
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="wrapper-buttons-switch">
          <div class="buttons">
            <div class="button outlined" id="room-id" data-id="323243">
              #323243
              <img src="/images/copy.svg" alt="">
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="button">
              <img src="/images/users-white.svg" alt="">
              Criar Sala
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="theme-switch-wrapper">
            <label class="theme-switch" for="checkbox">
            <input type="checkbox" id="checkbox" />
            <div class="slider round"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <main>
        <section id="question-form">
          <h2>Faça sua pergunta</h2>
          <form action="">
            <label class="sr-only" for="question">O que você quer perguntar?</label>
            <textarea name="question" id="question" 
            placeholder="O que você quer perguntar?"></textarea>
          <footer>
            <div>
              <img src="/images/lock.svg" alt="Imagem de um cadeado">
              Esta pergunta é anônima
            </div>
            <button class="button">Enviar</button>
          </footer>
          </form>
        </section>
        <section id="questions">
          <h2 class="sr-only">Perguntas</h2>
          <div class="questions">
            <div class="question-wrapper">
              <div class="question-content">
                <div class="user">
                  <img src="/images/user.svg" alt="Avatar anônimo">
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                  <p>Qual a diferença entre const, var e let no Javascript?</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="check" data-id="1">
                  <img src="/images/check.svg" alt="">
                  Marcar como lida
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="delete" data-id="1">
                  <img src="/images/trash.svg" alt="">
                  Excluir
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question-wrapper read">
              <div class="question-content">
                <div class="user">
                  <img src="/images/user.svg" alt="Avatar anônimo">
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                  <p>O que é Typescript?</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="check" data-id="2">
                  <img src="/images/check.svg" alt="">
                  Marcar como lida
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="delete" data-id="2">
                  <img src="/images/trash.svg" alt="">
                  Excluir
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question-wrapper">
              <div class="question-content">
                <div class="user">
                  <img src="/images/user.svg" alt="Avatar anônimo">
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                  <p>O que é Javascript?</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="check" data-id="3">
                  <img src="/images/check.svg" alt="">
                  Marcar como lida
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="delete" data-id="3">
                  <img src="/images/trash.svg" alt="">
                  Excluir
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question-wrapper">
              <div class="question-content">
                <div class="user">
                  <img src="/images/user.svg" alt="Avatar anônimo">
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aperiam voluptatibus minus culpa commodi natus, nobis incidunt error enim, veniam, nisi iusto. Eaque rerum consectetur modi error debitis laborum exercitationem iste!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="check" data-id="4">
                  <img src="/images/check.svg" alt="">
                  Marcar como lida
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="delete" data-id="4">
                  <img src="/images/trash.svg" alt="">
                  Excluir
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal-wrapper">
      <div class="modal">
        <h2>Excluir Pergunta</h2>
        <p>Tem certeza que você deseja excluir esta pergunta?</p>
        <form action="#" method="POST">
          <label class="sr-only" for="password">Digite sua senha</label>
          <input type="password" id="password" name="password" 
          placeholder="Digite sua senha">
          <div class="buttons">
            <div class="button gray cancel">Cancelar</div>
            <button class="button red">Sim, excluir</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
